name: Goobit
mes: Gira walks around a flash, white new laboratory. He passes by a couple of female scientists but ignores them, waiting for one of the tour scientists to come and take him through a tour of the lab...

name: Goobit
mes:
Gira leaned against the sterile white walls of the laboratory, his eyes scanning the surroundings. Female scientists in tight lab coats bustled around, their shapely legs partially revealed by the short hems of their skirts. Their creamy thighs and pert asses swayed with every step they took. He couldn't help but take notice, but he quickly refocused his mind back to the task at hand.

Finally, one of the tour scientists—a petite brunette with wide hips and a generous bust pushing against her buttoned-up lab coat—approached him. "Welcome, Mr. Gira," she said in a sultry voice, her green eyes glimmering with hidden intentions.

Gira stood up straight and nodded curtly. "Thank you. I'd like to see what goes on here, particularly any research involving biological entities."

The scientist gave a knowing smile, placing a hand on her hip. "You're in for an interesting tour," she replied, her eyes briefly glancing towards a restricted area guarded by intimidating security systems. "Shall we begin?"
